    • Enum Constant Detail

      • BAND

        public static final ID3v24FrameBodyEqualization.InterpolationMethod BAND
        No interpolation is made. A jump from one adjustment level to another occurs in the middle between two points on the EQ curve.

      • LINEAR

        public static final ID3v24FrameBodyEqualization.InterpolationMethod LINEAR
        Interpolation between adjustment points is linear. That is, a straight line is drawn between two points on the EQ curve.
